divs: sighting detailsat dawn on this morning of march the 17th, i was on way home when i saw a triangle shaped craft coming toward me, i pulled over to try to take a picture of it, it was moving quickly so i failed, i then proceeded to follow it toward highway 29\35 area of logansport it was going in a slightly north to southeast direction. was weird its lights where uniformly triangular, then all the sudden it changed from solid lights to very fast moving strobing all over lights.. i dont know what that means , it was low enough that when i pulled over and stuck my head out the window to see it, i should have heard it had it been a normal aircraft?
Summary: At Dawn, saw low flying bright lights, Triangle craft strobing light on front
